name: BMO Low Volatility US Equity ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide exposure to the performance of a portfolio of U.S. stocks that have lower sensitivity to market movements with the potential for long-term capital appreciation. The ETF will primarily invest in and hold equity securities of U.S. companies. Securities from the large capitalization U.S. equity universe that have lower sensitivity to market movement (beta) will be selected for the portfolio and will be weighted so that a higher allocation is given to securities with lower beta.
